---
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="avatar-container">
            <img src="images/ceesta_image_2.png" alt="ceesta Icon" class="avatar" />
        </div>
        <h1>ceesta</h1>
        <p class="tagline">大切なものを、光の籠に編み込んで。</p>
    </div>
</section>
<style>
    .hero {
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        position: relative;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1f2833 0%, #0b0c10 100%);
    }

    .hero-content {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .avatar-container {
        width: 180px;
        height: 180px;
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        padding: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-gold), var(--accent-cyan));
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(102, 252, 241, 0.2);
    }

    .avatar {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        border-radius: 50%;

        object-fit: cover;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .tagline {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--accent-cyan);
        letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
</style>